name: The Alien Xylophone.
description:
In 2301 a strange artifact is discovered in the Iberian desert, an uninhabited peninsula that was once Portugal and Spain. This strange looking artifact has 5 buttons, each corresponding to a very strange musical tone. It is definitely an extraterrestrial artifact. Perhaps a form of communication... who knows? Let's find out?

How to play?
Use mouse (fingers on mobile) or q,w,e,r,t keys!! COMBINE both!! :) HAVE FUN!!
